730243f-a.title: General view - East 34th Street - Northwest.
730243f-a.text:
A general view northwestward from the Harriet Hubbard Aver
Building at No. 321 E. 34th Shreet, north side, between First
and Second Avenue, showing skyscrapers of the 42nd Street -
Midtown area of aanhattan. Fromm left to right (across the three
views) they are: the 1O Naat 4Oth Street Building; the Lefcourt -
Colonial Building (under construction); the Lincoln Building;
the Chaain Building; and the Chrysler Buildipg.,under construction).
In the foreground is the Second Avenue ''E1'' with a corner
of St. Gabriels Park on the easterly side and tenements to the
west.
Sentember 10, 1929.
VieWs 1,2 and 3
P.L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
